<D>__{nice? it's more than nice. it's great to meet you. it's fantastic to meet you. i just, i can't tell you how glad i am. ralph. really. i am.}
<C>__{ralph}
<D>__{well, thank you, i've heard a lot of nice things about you too, and...}
<A>__{he rushes over to hug her.}
